p.description = "<p>Technology/Platform: Java\nDifficulty Level: Beginner</p>\n\n<p>Abstract: \u201cHello Data\u201d in 3D animated Java-loving glory. Learn to use Processing \u2013 a free Java IDE and library toolset for creating 3D &amp; 2D animated Java applets and standalone applications. If you can see your data, you can know your data, and have fun doing it!</p>\n\n<p>Presented By: Wes Faler</p>\n\n<p>About the Speaker: Wes Faler has 10110 years of professional programming experience and is a veteran of several commercial grid-computing applications. Wes is currently doing grid simulations for the US EPA, working with cloud computing, and finding every reason possible to use Processing.</p>";
